4.46 OEFormalPartialCharges 
 
   
void OEFormalPartialCharges(OEMolBase &amp;mol)
    
Set the partial charge property of each atom in a molecule to its
formal charge.  This is equivalent of calling OEAtomBase::SetPartialCharge
on every atom with the value return from OEAtomBase::GetFormalCharge.

  

  
          
     
        
